Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:55.88,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}今天是那樣燦爛奪目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.34,0:14:06.78,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}美麗得讓人鼻酸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:11.15,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}甚至感到心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:20.78,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}即使有那麼多那麼多人
