Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:17.05,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}因為害怕改變
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:21.11,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}或許有些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:25.93,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}或許會有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:31.32,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}只有去看看才會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:39.55,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}來吧 向前一步走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:45.78,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}想要實現大大的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:50.13,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}嚮往遙遠的遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:54.75,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}想要在純白的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:59.76,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}留下最初的足跡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:09.21,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}太陽在世界的盡頭翻滾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:19.80,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}南風終將越過小島 吹動每一根頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.82,0:18:31.32,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}想要實現好大的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:35.87,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}嚮往遙遠的遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:40.52,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}在海浪中顛簸談笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:45.38,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}不斷往前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:49.86,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}向著比宇宙更遙遠的地方
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,staff1,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.25,0:00:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,值日生遲到會給大家添麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的菜單交給你寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…剩菜大雜燴？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.59,0:00:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,太直接了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.41,0:00:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這種時候就要像平時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.25,0:00:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs30\c&H645D50&\frz7.82\pos(564,134)}今 日 菜 單
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.25,0:00:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs30\c&HBC615F&\frz7.82\pos(534,268)}南極風味{\c&H645D50&}豬肉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.25,0:00:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs25\c&H645D50&\pos(380,458)\frz1.872}鹹魚串也要吃哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.25,0:00:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs30\c&H645D50&\frz1.365\pos(778,498)}還有豬肉蓋飯和豬肉湯套餐!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.25,0:00:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs30\c&H645D50&\frz2.109\pos(708,604)}洗碗:{\c&H7A6CE1&}B{\c&H645D50&}隊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.14,0:00:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我們值日生的通知就這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,大家還有什麼意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 自製的可爾必思口味太淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.03,0:00:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,誒 太濃了才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,窮人可爾必思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,別說窮字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.55,0:00:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,值日生 請講
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 這是昨天的值日生做的 跟我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我會認真參考的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.18,0:00:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.38,0:00:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟說了風大嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,之後還要幹啥來著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.57,0:01:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,洗廁所！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.34,0:01:14.97,Default,,500,0,450,,{\bord0\c&H5D5049&}距夏隊返程還有{\c&H513899&}3{\c&H5D5049&}天！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.66,0:01:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,都說我討厭羊棲菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,別抱怨了 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.21,0:01:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,保奈美小姐你都有貧血的苗頭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,壞心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.88,0:01:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,唉 剛來的時候還是可愛的女高中生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.64,0:01:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她們現在又沒有在做女高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,要茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.52,0:01:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要是沉迷南極太久 會回歸不了社會的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就像那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,七索 糊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,立直一發三色寶牌寶牌…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 是裏寶牌裏寶牌 三倍滿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}都叫你不要信搭子了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得那是另一回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.39,0:01:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,聽到吸塵器的聲音就感覺像是在家裡一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:01:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,有人邀請我 我就採訪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 島內散步？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天也有人帶我和報瀨去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 說一聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你今天值日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你被排擠啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哼 島內散步算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我之後可是要去鑿冰的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.71,0:02:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 對了 得抓緊才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,集合時間就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,鑿冰是全員參加的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.74,0:02:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,同行者4人 將前往參加鑿冰 請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了 請注意安全
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,該坐哪輛？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 是冰山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,要鑿這麼大的冰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這是在禁止外帶的南極唯一可以自由帶走的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這些冰裡封存著數萬年前的空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一融化就會滋滋地爆開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要吃吃看？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,要！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是幾萬年前的空氣的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你吃得出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,等我成年了 一定要拿它配酒喝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺你喝醉了會超級話癆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,一開始鑿冰 就會有種夏天要結束了的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就會進入秋天 進入冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.59,0:03:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,要越冬啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,冬天都做些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,做很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:58.84,Default,,600,0,0,,{\an8\fs30}流水素麵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:03:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,比如做遊戲 喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,研究和觀測當然也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不過畢竟六月以後就整天都是晚上了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,對了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是叫「極夜」來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,接近中午時地平線會亮一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一天裡就只有這一點變化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的時間就只有無盡的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,一直是晚上啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不過相應地 可以看到很漂亮的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,還能看到極光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,極光…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 說起來沒看到！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,因為天還只有一點黑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,和企鵝拍紀念照 吃刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,極光和南極星都還沒看到！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,都說了現在是極晝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,救我 不過好幸福！不過好臭！不過好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好臭 臭也很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,她在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回去幹活了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你們就慢慢休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這大概也是你們看冰海的最後機會了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,對了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫你救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可是不能靠近5米之內啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,想想辦法啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺完全習慣這片風景了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我假設一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就是假設一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.97,0:05:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說 反正還有空房間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡也能一直傳影片回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不是現在非回去不可吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你肯定是打算弄痛我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不會不會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你騙人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,廢話 要是現在不回去 今年之內就別想回了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的啦 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,天黑的話我有信心睡到天昏地暗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,上學怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,等你回去的時候大家全都畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,還有家人怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,小結的電視劇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不過嘛 不想回去的心情我也能理解…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那你會再來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,來越冬哦 我們四個人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,說定了哦 不許拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,明白明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.44,0:06:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那就行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來 我們要怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,隊長不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們把最後想做的事都提出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,最後啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真的這樣就行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯！最後我們想和這裡的所有人一起玩
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,（IN-One Step）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.53,0:07:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}打飛！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}阿敏加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}加油上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,隊長！我要是打中了 你能重新考慮一下嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己答應的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他還沒死心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,打得中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,沒戲的 阿吟可是人稱「南極的豎紋19號」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs27}註：日本知名棒球隊球衣多為豎紋 19號是許多名投手的球衣號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,投出的球可是一級品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,誰都躲不開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,貴子還是打到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,貴子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你在看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,日向！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,（Partb）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,現在才剪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,要剪來的時候就剪不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺現在想剪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.27,0:08:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我來剪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你就別湊熱鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要剪多短？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你確定？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.31,0:08:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:55.05,Default,,0,0,100,,{\an8\bord0\c&HD4B170&\fad(300,0)}夏隊{\c&H686561&}辛苦了{\c&H763EA0&}！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你要磨蹭到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,她可真要走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\3c&HF4F9F8&\c&HCFA968&}夏隊{\c&H6E5D54&}辛苦了{\c&H863F9F&}！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.07,0:09:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H826758&\3c&HF4F6E9&\fs35\frz350.1\pos(498,322)\fad(0,300)}南極挑戰 女高中生記者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H706C6F&\3c&HEEF4F5&\fs35\move(438,709,406,516)\frz331.7}回到日本也別忘了我們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H706C6F&\3c&HEEF4F5&\fs35\pos(406,516)\frz331.7}回到日本也別忘了我們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這個橫幅是手工的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 主角來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,來 到這裡排成一排
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 適合我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是母女 笑起來一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,她怎麼了？失戀了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 某種意義上說可能是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,哪種意義上？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你猜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,猜不到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,按照慣例 今天舉行的應該是越冬交替儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但由於今年沒有人需要交替
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,所以改為夏隊的歸國送行儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 請隊長講話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,今天天氣晴朗 是個啟程的好日子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其本次是日本第一次有女高中生科考隊員在南極生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這是一次很大的嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信她們一定很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也非常非常不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但是她們出色地完成了科考隊員的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以聽到所有男隊員心裡都在大聲呼喊 希望她們留下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但是她們還是要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,請你們死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,最後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這段時間以來謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,回去之後 希望你們能偶爾想起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:11:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在遙遠天空的另一邊 伸手不見五指的黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,默默越冬的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們再次在這裡相會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 請夏隊代表小淵澤報瀨講話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都知道 我的母親是一位南極科考隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,看著非常喜歡南極 為南極著迷而離家的她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我對南極的印象並不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我是為了解開自己心裡的這個疙瘩而來到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,比宇宙更遙遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,媽…不 我的母親是這樣描述這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這是一個暴露一切的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,時間 生物 心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這是一片沒有任何東西保護我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒有地方可以躲藏的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在這裡暴露出了所有不堪的 想要隱瞞的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,流著淚水和毫無掩飾的自己坦誠相對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,一起把它們逐一克服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,然後我覺得我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,母親之所以熱愛這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為她和熱愛這片景色 這片天空 這股風一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,熱愛能夠和夥伴們一起克服艱難險阻的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:13:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,熱愛這個沒有任何干擾 只能和夥伴們一起去克服的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛這片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,請大家努力越冬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定會再到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你哭了？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,（IN-宇宙を見上げて）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你做給我們的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,用的是剩餘的材料就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,請把這個交給等在日本的阿悠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,…啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,表走啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你酒味好重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這種日子怎能不喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不用管她 這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,報瀨 說謝謝啊 說謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,別縮了 上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 結月你簽名是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好像偶像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,賣了多少張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你們能不能別七嘴八舌了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.70,0:14:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我很期待你的電視劇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然要回去了才能看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有人期待的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那還用說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你得加油才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.49,0:15:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,保重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝您！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,該道謝的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,還記得我一開始在麵包車裡對你們說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,和當時的你們聊了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我很受鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,看到你們 我就決心一定不能讓計劃中止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.93,0:15:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,原來當時快中止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,大人呢 有時候是不能坦白的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,隊長就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,聽見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,現在很敢說話了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 上去吧上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,還有 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺如果不跟你一起越冬 媽媽會怪我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經不需要它了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,她們走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,平均年齡一下子上去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 接下來的日子還長著呢！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,（IN-ハルカトオク）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord0\c&H5D6872&\frz347.2\move(170,489,191,444)}發件匣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,剛來的時候還覺得特別遠呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,旅行就是這樣的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒有結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,還要再經歷一次60度50度40度…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,尖叫！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定又要吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,隨便啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,再吐個好多次 覺得難受得想死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼關係呢 這也是旅行的一部分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.68,0:17:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有沒有覺得我們變強了一點？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,應該說是變野了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,因為這裡的一切都太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要穿這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,最後一次了嘛 肯定還是要穿這個才帶感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 富有吸引力 逗趣且動 動人的報導就要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,還是臨場發揮更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好 要開拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,誒 就要拍了？等一下 最後一次了 我再看一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是極光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 拍不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.73,0:18:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事有個一兩回也無妨嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H55514F&\an7\fs25\pos(549,180)\frz352.6}媽媽\N{\b0}真的比這還要漂亮一萬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H55514F&\an7\fs30\pos(420,263)}媽媽\N{\b0}真的比這還要漂亮一萬倍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那個就是南極星 就這麼定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.51,0:19:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得應該沒那麼亮…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,（ED）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在這裡分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,麻利…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意思是 我們不能再在一起了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,相反 即使我們不在一起 也能夠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.72,0:21:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因為 我們已經是我們了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.24,0:21:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼名言啊 你變成日向了？
